  "prompt": "Is there any dual SIM mobile supporting 4G or 4G and 3G?",
  "response": "Yes, there are many dual SIM mobile phones that support 4G or a combination of 4G and 3G on different slots. Many modern smartphones feature dual SIM capabilities, allowing users to use two separate SIM cards in one device. This functionality often supports 4G connectivity on both slots, but sometimes it supports 4G on one slot and 3G on the other.\n\nPopular brands like Samsung, Xiaomi, OnePlus, Huawei, and others offer models with dual SIM capabilities and support for 4G networks. It's always a good idea to check the specific model's specifications to ensure it meets your network support requirements, as dual SIM configurations and network support can vary between models and regions.",
